articles.author: Hafsa Adil
articles.title: Qatar keep AFC Asian Cup trophy at home with 3-1 win over Jordan - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Qatar became the first country in 20 years to win back-to-back Asian Cup titles with a 3-1 win over Jordan.
